<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,260,356]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
Only known from the King George River in the Kimberley (
<figureCitation box="[823,905,260,284]" captionStart="FIGURE 19" captionStartId="39.[151,250,1147,1170]" captionTargetBox="[262,1325,197,1124]" captionTargetId="figure-23@39.[258,1329,193,1126]" captionTargetPageId="39" captionText="FIGURE 19. Distribution of Melanotaenia exquisita in the Kimberley." pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Fig. 19</figureCitation>
