<emphasis box="[926,1189,260,284]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Melanotaenia exquisita</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is also found in tributaries of a number of 
<collectingRegion box="[396,603,295,319]" country="Australia" name="Northern Territory" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Northern Territory</collectingRegion>
rivers, including the Katherine, Edith, Mary, South Alligator and Fergusson (
